":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dd8961d6fcbd69c181784734d82e1992543a10","tid":1853684,"uid":161157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591be5b6e3d0a3221f944f336eb0a7b5f277a0ba","tid":1853684,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"你點屌都冇用<br />\n黑警理撚得你<br />\n佢地要有實質後果先會驚"},{"pid":"f166ab15ecce2f0a4b9083c9ec8ab22d9811945c","tid":1853684,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be8de35032d03190699241b92419aeaf21c7268","tid":1853684,"uid":35045,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"佢地套裝仲好過醫護人員..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"有槍"},{"pid":"f88ab680509fa423cc7da152609ce446b1b4a3f9","tid":1853684,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4257c6a8e9ec27912d72bc68ce898bce3f0ef3f4","tid":1853684,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLG5hw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLG5hw9.jpg&h=193bad8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gk8CS5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGk8CS5w.jpg&h=556f935f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐耀佳表示，無國界醫生及紅十字國際委員會也要求戰地醫院內不准有武裝，他自己多年在戰地醫院服務的經驗，也是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即使例如軍人想進入醫院，也要先卸除武裝，軍人也尊重及遵守有關做法。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n他指，因若一方派別持武裝進入醫院，可能挑起另一方會同樣做法，或會在醫院內引起衝突，危害病人及醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n他指，香港公立醫院內會有警崗，警員會有佩槍，或押解犯人到醫院的警員也會有佩槍，但有關情況是一般值勤。而昨晚在屯門醫院內情況並非一般值勤，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「想表示咩嘢，想威嚇人呀」。醫院內仍有其他病人及家屬，「一行出嚟見到咁多警察攞住槍，你唔驚呀」。他直斥警方做法是「一係驚到無槍會頂唔順」、「一係靠嚇」、「一係無知」，質疑連第三世界武裝衝突地方，軍人都會遵守的事情，香港警察卻沒有遵守</span></span>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"Twitter 幫佢！"}]}